{"url":"https://www.makeuseof.com/best-laptops-for-students/","title":"The Best Laptops for Students of 2024","subtitle":"Heading back to class? Pack one of these laptops to take with you.","heroImageUrl":"https://static0.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/52782153236_36d2178802_o.jpg?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop","items":[{"rank":1,"heading":"Best Laptop for Students Overall: Dell XPS 13 (9340)","body":"Credit: Dell The Dell XPS 13 9340 is a reliable choice for students. It’s a very capable laptop and can handle demanding tasks, such as video editing, multitasking, and even gaming when you’ve finished studying for the day. It may not quite boast the same power and features as the latest 9345 model with its integrated AI and SnapDragon X processor, but the jury is still out on these CoPilot+ Microsoft laptops. The 9340’s sleek, lightweight design ensures it’s easy to carry around campus, and the 13.4-inch size slips seamlessly into a backpack. Additionally, the bright, anti-reflective display ","imageUrl":"https://static0.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dell-xps-13-9340.jpg?q=49&fit=crop&w=825&dpr=2"},{"rank":2,"heading":"Best Budget Laptop for Students: Inspiron 15","body":"The older model of the Inspiron 15 is now available at a much reduced price. At this rock-bottom rate, you can expect the laptop to be suitable for everyday tasks such as web browsing, word processing, and light multitasking. However, while more expensive, the new Inspiron 15 3535 model still falls within the budget price range and offers some excellent value specs. Various processors are available, but the AMD Ryzen 7 7730U variation is a good option for students with heavier workloads. It also has 16GB of DDR4 RAM and 1TB SSD storage. The non-touch display of this model has a Full HD resolut","imageUrl":"https://static0.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/inspiron-15.jpg?q=49&fit=crop&w=825&dpr=2"},{"rank":3,"heading":"Best 2-in-1: Lenovo Yoga 9i","body":"Credit: Lenovo With its sleek, premium design and compact build, the Lenovo Yoga 9i is ideal for students who seek portability and the versatility of a 2-in-1 design. It features a pleasing 14-inch 2880x1800 OLED touchscreen with a 120Hz refresh rate that delivers visuals and color ideal for media consumption or for students who need extra detail and color accuracy for their studies. With 16GB of LPDDR5X RAM and a 512GB SSD, the base configuration of this laptop gives you smooth performance for multitasking and anyone involved in creative projects. For a little extra, students can opt for 32GB","imageUrl":"https://static0.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lenovo-yoga-9i.jpg?q=49&fit=crop&w=825&dpr=2"},{"rank":4,"heading":"Best Chromebook for Students: Acer Chromebook Spin 714","body":"Credit: Acer While it’s not the cheapest Chromebook you can find, the Acer Chromebook Spin 714 is an excellent midrange option with features that justify the price. It offers students cloud-based studying on a durable 2-in-1 laptop. Additionally, it’s lightweight at just slightly over 3lbs, and a 360-degree hinge means you can seamlessly swap between laptop and tablet modes. The 14-inch touchscreen has a 1920x1200p resolution, which makes media content good to watch and documents and websites sharp and easy on the eye. This base design (CP714-2W-56B2 model) features a 13th-generation Intel Cor","imageUrl":"https://static0.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/acer-chromebook-spin-714.jpg?q=49&fit=crop&w=825&dpr=2"},{"rank":5,"heading":"Best MacBook for Students: MacBook Air 13-inch M3","body":"Credit: Apple Over the years, the go-to MacBook for many students has been the MacBook Air 13-inch. It’s now graced with the M3 chip, which ensures it’s still the best choice with its predecessor-trumping performance. Additionally, it maintains the same streamlined, stylish design, lightweight build, and stunning 13.6-inch Liquid Retina display. However, for many, the M3 chip offers a minimal performance upgrade. With the MacBook Air 13-inch M2 available at a more affordable price now, it may provide better value for students, especially as it was only in 2023 that it received all the plaudits","imageUrl":"https://static0.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/macbook-air-13-inch-m3.jpg?q=49&fit=crop&w=825&dpr=2"}],"branding":{"domain":"www.makeuseof.com","siteName":"MakeUseOf","logoUrl":"https://static0.makeuseofimages.com/assets/images/muo-logo-full-colored-light.svg?v=3.6","logoDataUrl":"data:image/png;base64,","faviconUrl":"https://www.makeuseof.com/public/build/images/favicon-48x48.png","themeColor":null,"accentColor":"#c60c0c","accentSource":"logo","fontFamily":null},"fetchedVia":"fetch"}